Subject: Current status and next steps — Compliance AI initiatives

Hi [Manager Name],

Here’s a concise update on the current situation and proposed next steps:

- Client summary generation (Lot 1)
    - Auto-generate per‑alert client syntheses from UGO/HUGO via Domino.
    - Estimated gain ~4 minutes per dossier, ~26k dossiers/year. Initial ROI ~1–2 FTE across FR/PT. Data structure is ready and clean.[[1]](https://www.notion.so/Cardif-2844c5258b4b8091b124fede73931eda?pvs=21)
- Automated comment drafting (Lot 2)
    - AI drafts analyst comments for LOD1 alerts. Analyst reviews/edits before submission. Larger gains expected on reinforced reviews (0.74 FTE estimate).[[1]](https://www.notion.so/Cardif-2844c5258b4b8091b124fede73931eda?pvs=21)
- Architecture and data flow
    - UGO/HUGO sends JSON to Domino. Domino returns results to a dedicated table for UI display. No direct writes to prod. Three test environments available.[[1]](https://www.notion.so/Cardif-2844c5258b4b8091b124fede73931eda?pvs=21)
- Confidentiality approach
    - Avoid names in LLM context. HUGO adds names post‑generation. Sensitive flags handled generically (e.g., “client has a sensitivity”).[[1]](https://www.notion.so/Cardif-2844c5258b4b8091b124fede73931eda?pvs=21)
- Procedures chatbot (RAG)
    - Current behavior over‑focuses on a single document and over‑summarizes. Plan to adjust retrieval breadth and prompting. Potential uplift with stronger model if justified.[[1]](https://www.notion.so/Cardif-2844c5258b4b8091b124fede73931eda?pvs=21)
- IG reports summarization via Power Automate / Copilot
    - PA flow demoed end‑to‑end; Copilot license availability under discussion. Option: Domino reads SharePoint PDFs and returns syntheses back to tracking lists.[[1]](https://www.notion.so/Cardif-2844c5258b4b8091b124fede73931eda?pvs=21)
- Access and modeling
    - Domino Cardiff access requested for specific projects. Existing classic models in place (LR, RF, XGBoost) with interest in selective GenAI testing on transactions.[[1]](https://www.notion.so/Cardif-2844c5258b4b8091b124fede73931eda?pvs=21)

Proposed next steps

- Submit Lots 1–2 to the committee for validation and budget gating.[[1]](https://www.notion.so/Cardif-2844c5258b4b8091b124fede73931eda?pvs=21)
